ports.behavior:
forward policy
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from policy
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from email_body_and_header
assign Level.High if Level.High from policy
assign Level.High if Level.High from email_body_and_header

forward bob_private_key
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from bob_private_key
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from policy
assign Level.High if Level.High from bob_private_key
assign Level.High if Level.High from policy

forward bob_pub_key
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from bob_pub_key
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from email_body_and_header
assign Level.High if Level.High from bob_pub_key
assign Level.High if Level.High from email_body_and_header

forward email_body_and_header_and_bob_pub_key
assign LevelBeforeEncryption.High if Level.High from email_body_and_header_and_bob_pub_key
assign LevelBeforeEncryption.Low if Level.Low from email_body_and_header_and_bob_pub_key
unset Level.High
set Level.Low

forward email_body_encrypted_and_header_and_bob_private_key
assign Level.High if LevelBeforeEncryption.High from email_body_encrypted_and_header_and_bob_private_key
assign Level.Low if LevelBeforeEncryption.Low from email_body_encrypted_and_header_and_bob_private_key

forward bob_private_key
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from bob_private_key
assign Level.Low if Level.Low from email_body_encrypted_and_header
assign Level.High if Level.High from bob_private_key
assign Level.High if Level.High from email_body_encrypted_and_header
